{
  "stem": "1684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the parents-- Rosen was their name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rosen and Horowitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's in the book there, too, if you read the book.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, their stories are in there too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were taken back to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we worked by-- by, in Brunnlitz, we worked there until 1945, May the 9th, 1945.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then a guy on a horse came, a Russian guy, and he said you are free.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, this can't be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I-- they told us not to go out, not to walk out from the camp, because they were shooting all over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans were running away, and, of course, Schindler went away, and we were all by ourselves there in the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said we had to clean the camp now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I just wanted to see how the outside looks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was going out and I said, oh there's a world outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, I didn't believe that I ever will see daylight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went out, and a German woman who was living next door approached me, and she said, would you like to move into my house?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I have a husband and a brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have to come with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we moved into that house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were staying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then she opened up the kitchen-- she had a-- she was German, she had-- everything was clean.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said I should bake a cake if I want.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- you see, Schindler took over a magazine from a Jewish guy who had fabrics.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Schindler said that whoever leaves when-- when the war is over, they should get some coupons-- some-- some fabrics.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had some fabrics, we all got some fabrics.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
